value.string: Residential building lot located in the quiet country town of Maunaloa. Walk to nearby General Store and Post Office. West side beaches are a short 10 minute drive. Main town is about a 20 minute drive

Level home site located on Hoaikane Street in the charming country town of Maunaloa. The property has sweeping ocean views. Enjoy the amazing sunsets from the property. Walk to nearby Maunaloa Village for the General Store and Post Office. Beaches are about 4 miles away. Airport is 16 miles away and Kaunakakai town is 20 miles

Level residential building lot on the top street in Maunaloa Village. Wide open ranch lands across the street and unobstructed ocean views. The sunsets from the property are amazing. The neighborhood is well established and the lot is situated toward at end of the street where it is quiet.

Level home site located on Kaana Street in Maunaloa. The property opens up to a greenbelt and rolling ranch lands. Can be purchased with D-101 to combine for a larger building lot. Papohaku Beach is about 4 miles away. It is about a 20 minute drive to the main town of Kaunakakaki. Walk to the General Store & Post Office. The climate is ideal with cool evening and warm sunny days.

Level home site located on Kaana Street in Maunaloa. Property opens up to a greenbelt and rolling ranch lands. Can be purchased with Lot D-100 to combine for a larger building lot. Beaches are 4 miles to Papohaku Beach Park. You are about 20 minutes to the main town of Kaunakakai.

OWNER FINANCING AVAILABLE with 20% down, 5% interest to qualified buyers Great starter lot in Kaunakai, Molokai. Close to the town's shops, hospital, and the wharf, where you can catch the twice daily ferry to Lahaina, Maui, or sail out to rich fishing grounds. Enjoy the Old Hawaii--like going back 50 years in time to when there was no traffic (sorry, no traffic lights!), few tourists, and no highrises...yet only 10 minutes to the airport and 20 minute flights to Honolulu shopping or Maui's activities.
Ready to build lot with bougainvillea and water meter. Short drive to one of the longest white sand beaches in the state. Fabulous sunset views, open pasture, shoreline, island and ocean views.

One of four lots for sale 1. 5 miles east of Kaunakakai. Two properties are on the main road and 2 lots are in back and have their own access to the highway. The back two properties back up to a fishpond. Slight slope on front two lots and level on back two lots. Buy them all an have over 1.25 acres for $425,000. One of the lots does have a water meter installed. These lots have all been cleared. Excellent level building lot fronting ancient fishpond. Fishpond being restored by www.kahonuamomona.org Ka Nonua Momona received grant money from OHA to clear mangrove on the Kaloko'eli Fishpond.

Kaluakoi fairway lots are as close to ocean front as you can get on west molokai with out being on the sand! Direct frontage on the now closed golf course provides for a wide open feel with the ease of only a 1/4 acre of maintaiance - all utilities are to the lot and ready for hook up. This is the best easiest building lot on the island. Short walk to white sand beaches, great snorkeling, shore fishing and quality surfing!!
